title: Zelda.Roms.and.Emulators
description:
This is my first upload. Hope you enjoy

To play SNES rom
Unzip Rom Folder
Open Zsnesw emulator
click config>input and configure your keyboard/controller/joypad however you like
click game>load -- find the files you unzipped and enjoy!

To play n64 games!!
Install Project64 application.
load the roms in much the same way as you did for SNES . be sure to config your controller or you will get frustrated.
